# SPA fallback rules for client-side routing (Cloudflare Pages)
# Dynamic routes served by static pages with client-side URL parsing
/join/*      /join/index.html       200
/session/*   /session/index.html    200
/callback/*  /callback/index.html   200
/dashboard/* /dashboard/index.html  200

# Catch-all SPA fallback
/*           /index.html            200
